premise_source_doc_sentence: Finn Wolfhard is a Canadian actor and voice actor .
He is best known for his starring role as Mike Wheeler in the supernatural Netflix series Stranger Things .
Finn Wolfhard is a Canadian actor and voice actor .
The appearance of Finn as an adult was based on Howard Keel 's character from the 1954 musical Seven Brides for Seven Brothers , which is a favorite of episode co-storyboarder Wolfhard .

The first season stars Winona Ryder , David Harbour , Finn Wolfhard , Millie Bobby Brown , Gaten Matarazzo , Caleb McLaughlin , Natalia Dyer , Charlie Heaton , Cara Buono , and Matthew Modine , with Noah Schnapp and Joe Keery in recurring roles .
Jeremy Ray Taylor , Sophia Lillis , Finn Wolfhard , Wyatt Oleff , Chosen Jacobs , Jack Dylan Grazer , Nicholas Hamilton , and Jackson Robert Scott are all featured in supporting roles .
Oliver Sava of The A.V. Club wrote positively of the way the episode focused on character development , noting that the episode bore similarities to both The Wizard of Oz and Captain America .
